OL,3,CMore funds to support Tata steel
OL,4,Cworkers and businesses
OL,6,FThe Government has announced it is
OL,7,Fdoubling funds to support workers and
OL,8,Fbusinesses affected by job losses at a
OL,9,Fgiant Tata steel plant.
OL,11,FMinisters said an extra #15 million
OL,12,Fwill be made available for supply
OL,13,Fchain businesses and workers affected
OL,14,Fby changes at Tata's Port Talbot site
OL,15,Fin south Wales.
OL,17,FWelsh Secretary Jo Stevens said the
OL,18,Fmove means a fund to support
OL,19,Fbusinesses across Wales heavily
OL,20,Freliant on Tata steel will be
OL,21,Fincreased to #30 million.
