OL,3,CMore funds to support Tata steel
OL,4,Cworkers and businesses
OL,6,FThe increase in funding is in
OL,7,Fanticipation of more people leaving
OL,8,FTata in early 2025 through the
OL,9,Fcompany's voluntary redundancy scheme.
OL,11,FMs Stevens said: "This Government is
OL,12,Facting decisively to support workers
OL,13,Fand businesses in Port Talbot.
OL,15,F"We are doubling the funding available
OL,16,Fto businesses and workers and widening
OL,17,Faccess to grants to ensure we support
OL,18,Fas many people as possible.
