OL,6,F"In just four months we have announced
OL,7,Fmore than #40 million in investment.
OL,8,FWe said we would back workers and
OL,9,Fbusinesses affected by the transition
OL,10,Fat Port Talbot and we are doing
OL,11,Fexactly that.
OL,13,F"While this remains a very difficult
OL,14,Ftime for Tata workers, their families
OL,15,Fand the community, we are determined
OL,16,Fto support workers and businesses in
OL,17,Four Welsh steel industry, whatever
OL,18,Fhappens."
